Installation instructions
*************************

If you wish to use @{b}Installer@{ub} then @{b}TSMorph@{ub} can be installed using the
supplied script. If not then the following is a description of what the
script does.

   @{b}*@{ub} 1) Make a new drawer for the executables - default @{b}Work:TSMorph@{ub},

   @{b}*@{ub} 2) Copy @{b}TSMorph@{ub}, @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub}, @{b}TSMorph.doc@{ub}, @{b}TSMorph.guide@{ub},
     @{b}TSMorph-prefs@{ub} and the @{b}Rexx@{ub} drawer and its contents and all their
     icons to the drawer created in 1) above (if you have a 68020/030
     with 68881/2 then copy the FPU version @{b}TSMorph-render.881@{ub} and
     rename it as @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub} instead of copying @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub}, or
     if you have a 68040 then copy the 040 version @{b}TSMorph-render.040@{ub}
     and rename it as @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub} instead of copying @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub})

   @{b}*@{ub} 3) If required copy the @{b}Brush@{ub} and @{b}Cursor@{ub} drawers and contents.

   @{b}*@{ub} 4) Make new drawers @{b}ENVARC:TSMorph@{ub} and @{b}ENV:TSMorph@{ub},

   @{b}*@{ub} 5) Copy the @{b}default Icons@{ub} to the directories created above.

   @{b}*@{ub} 6) Amend your @{b}s:user-startup@{ub} to assign @{b}TSMorph:@{ub} to the drawer
     created in step 1).

   @{b}*@{ub} 7) Manually perform the assign in step 6).

   @{b}*@{ub} 8) If you are running system version 3.0 (or greater) change the
     default tool for @{b}TSMorph.guide@{ub} to @{b}MultiView@{ub}.

   @{b}*@{ub} 9) If required copy the @{b}Tutorial@{ub} directory to @{b}TSMorph:@{ub}.

   @{b}*@{ub} 10) If required copy the @{b}HTML@{ub} directory to @{b}TSMorph:@{ub}, also copy the
     @{b}View_HTML@{ub} icon and use an editor to make the file contain:

         CD HTML
         Path:Mosaic file://localhost/TSMorph:html/TSMorph.html
     
             Where Path:Mosaic is the location of your version of Mosaic.

