@Prev "I-gad"
@Toc "Info"

Menus on the Info Window
========================

The following menus are available on the Information Window:


 @{" Project  " Link "I-men-P"}             Project menu

 @{" Settings " Link "men-Settings"}             Settings menu


@EndNode

@Node "I-men-P" "TSMorph.guide/I-men-P"
@Toc "I-men"

Info Window Project menu
------------------------

This menu contains the following items with their associated Amiga
short-cuts in the Info Window:


 @{" New         N " Link "I-men-P-New"}                    Create a new project
 @{" Open...     O " Link "I-men-P-Open"}                    Open a file

 @{" Save        S " Link "I-men-P-Save"}                    Save file
 @{" Save As...    " Link "I-men-P-Save_As"}                    Save named file
 @{" Delete...     " Link "I-men-P-Delete"}                    Delete a Project

 @{" About...      " Link "I-men-P-About"}                    Show about requester

 @{" Quit        Q " Link "I-men-P-Quit"}                    Quit program

 @{" Preview...    " Link "I-men-P-Preview"}                    Preview render
 @{" Edit Points E " Link "I-men-P-Edit_Points"}                    Open windows to edit points


@EndNode

