Info Window Project/Delete... menu item
.......................................

This can be used to delete a Project. It will delete the main file, its
icon (if present) and any associated Anim points files.

See @{"File Format" Link "File_Format"}.


@EndNode

@Node "I-men-P-About" "TSMorph.guide/I-men-P-About"
@Next "I-men-P-Quit"
