@Node "History" "TSMorph.guide/History"
@Next "Hints"
@Prev "Hard-Software"
@Toc "Main"

Version History (since 2.0)
***************************

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 3.2

        @{b}*@{ub} Recompiled using SAS/C 6.55. Runs about 3% faster.

        @{b}*@{ub} TSMorph.guide now looks almost OK under AmigaGuide 3.1.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 3.1

        @{b}*@{ub} Fixed the installer script to run correctly on all
          processors. (Thanks to Olivier Jeannet).

        @{b}*@{ub} Fixed the Rexx scripts to run correctly when running in ram
          in the 24bit address space. (Thanks to Olivier Jeannet).

        @{b}*@{ub} Help gadget now works better.

        @{b}*@{ub} Some code fixes for more recent EGS versions.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 3.0

        @{b}*@{ub} Recompiled using SAS/C 6.51.

        @{b}*@{ub} Added 68040 version.

        @{b}*@{ub} Now correctly handles AGA palettes.

        @{b}*@{ub} Installer now included. (Thanks to Perry Horner).

        @{b}*@{ub} Fixed a problem with the EGS pointer (Thanks to Darren
          Eveland).

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 2.5

        @{b}*@{ub} Major Enhancements

             @{b}*@{ub} Added @{b}EGS@{ub} support to @{"TSMorph" Link "P-EGS"} and @{"TSMorph-render" Link "P-EGS-R"}.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added @{"INTEGER" Link "P-INTEGER"} parameter to @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub}. This should
               make the program run faster, but the output will not be
               as good. The Icon supplied for the non FPU version has
               @{b}INTEGER=YES@{ub} set by default, the default @{"preview" Link "AR-Preview"} script
               also sets this.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added @{"MODEs" Link "P-MODE"} 4 to 31. This changes the @{"Settings" Link "men-Settings"} menu.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added @{"Triangulate" Link "CI-men-E-Triangulate"} menu item to convert point links to
               triangles. Points can now be linked to up to 16 other
               points.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added a short tutorial - See
               @{"Tutorial/Tutorial.readme" ALINK
               "Tutorial/Tutorial.readme/Main"}.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added documentation in plain text format - See
               @{"TSMorph.doc" ALINK "TSMorph.doc/Main"}. (Thanks to Perry
               Horner).

             @{b}*@{ub} Added documentation in .html format - Mosaic is required
               to view this.

        @{b}*@{ub} Minor Enhancments

             @{b}*@{ub} Edited the graphics in this guide. It will only look
               correct under the OS3.0+ version of AmigaGuide.library.

             @{b}*@{ub} When trying to close the @{"Public Screen" Link "P-PUBSCREEN"} @{b}TSMorph@{ub} will
               display an @{"error" Link "Err-CScreen"} if any other windows are open.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"Horizontal" Link "E-gad-Horiz"} and @{"Vertical" Link "E-gad-Vert"} gadgets are now correct on 2
               colour screens.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added @{b}REQTOOLS@{ub} parameter to @{"TSMorph" Link "P-REQTOOLS"} and @{"TSMorph-render" Link "P-REQTOOLS-R"}.

             @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub} now uses @{b}nofrag.library@{ub} for memory
               allocation if available.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added new @{"prescript" Link "AR-Prescript"} example script to render all frames.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added new @{"Hints & Tips" Link "Hints"} section.

             @{b}*@{ub} Sped up the remapping of normal ILBM images.

             @{b}*@{ub} Install script now determines 68020/881 correctly itself.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added some new @{"ARexx" Link "AR"} scripts to generate animations.

        @{b}*@{ub} Bug Fixes

             @{b}*@{ub} Fixed a very silly bug with the @{"DEPTH" Link "P-DEPTH"} parameter. It was
               always read as at least 20. This should speed up
               rendering.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"TSMorph-prefs" Link "TSMP-men-E-ResetD"} and @{"TSMorph" Link "men-S-ResetD"} set @{"ANTIALIAS" Link "P-ANTIALIAS"} and @{"HELP" Link "P-HELP"}
               correctly when Reset to Defaults.

             @{b}*@{ub} Some fixes to the default @{"PREVIEW" Link "P-PREVIEW"} script. (Thanks to
               Stefan Haubenthal).

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"TSMorph-prefs" Link "TSMorph-prefs"} now correctly sets the @{"Render mode" Link "P-MODE"}.

             @{b}*@{ub} Output images should not have garbage on the right hand
               side.

             @{b}*@{ub} Lots of minor code and docs changes.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 2.4

        @{b}*@{ub} Fixed bug where if 1st image for a Morph was loaded to
          convert the first frame then the second image was never
          loaded.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 2.3

        @{b}*@{ub} Enhancements

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"Keyboard" Link "E-Key"} shortcuts added to @{"Edit" Link "Edit"} windows to change
               @{"Edit Mode" Link "EModes"} (this prevents any screen flicker when
               @{"CHANGEPALLETE" Link "P-CHANGEPALETTE"} is set to YES).

        @{b}*@{ub} Bug Fixes

             @{b}*@{ub} Sensible message is displayed if @{b}opal.library@{ub} is not
               present and an input image does not exist in
               @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub}.

             @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub} no longer attempts to load
               unnecessary images and point files for the first and
               last frames.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"PREVIEW" Link "P-PREVIEW"} can now be longer than the default value without
               causing public screen name problems.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"TSMorph-prefs" Link "TSMorph-prefs"} no longer resets preferences to defaults
               if @{"Open..." Link "TSMP-men-P-Open"} is cancelled.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"Zoom?" Link "P-ZOOM"} menu item now works on the @{"Info" Link "Info"} window.

             @{b}*@{ub} No longer opens project @{"SETTINGS=" Link "P-SETTINGS"} settings file twice.

             @{b}*@{ub} Title of file requester to @{"Open Project" Link "I-men-P-Open"} is now Load
               Project not Load File.

             @{b}*@{ub} Major source code clean up.

             @{b}*@{ub} Source code is now available. Distribution is under GNU
               General Public Licence.  See @{"distribution" Link "Distribution"}.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 2.2

        @{b}*@{ub} Major Enhancements

             @{b}*@{ub} Added @{"Anti-Alias" Link "P-ANTIALIAS"} capability to @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub}.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added ability to @{b}TSMorph@{ub} and @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub} to load a
               large variety of image formats (JPEG, ILBM (including 24
               bit, EHB, HAM6, HAM8 and DCTV with @{b}dctv.library@{ub}), TARGA,
               GIF and PPM). See @{"OPENMODE" Link "P-OPENMODE"} and @{"LOADSCRIPT" Link "P-LOADSCRIPT"}.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added a lot more @{"save formats" Link "P-SAVEFORMAT"} (grey 16, grey 256, HAM 6,
               HAM 8 and DCTV3 and DCTV4 [with @{b}dctv.library@{ub}]).

             @{b}*@{ub} Added continuous @{"help" Link "P-HELP"} option, and @{"Help Text" Link "I-gad-Help"} gadget to
               @{b}TSMorph@{ub}.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added the @{"Preview" Link "AR-Preview"} option to preview render an image. See
               @{"Preview..." Link "I-men-P-Preview"}, @{"Preview..." Link "CI-men-P-Preview"} and @{"PREVIEW" Link "P-PREVIEW"}.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added the ability to open @{"custom" Link "P-CUSTOMMODE"} screens.

             @{b}*@{ub} Can now save the first and last images - see @{"Prescript" Link "AR-Prescript"}.

             @{b}*@{ub} Added preferences editor @{"TSMorph-prefs" Link "TSMorph-prefs"}.

        @{b}*@{ub} Minor Enhancements

             @{b}*@{ub} Loading Image requester is displayed. See @{"OPENMODE" Link "P-OPENMODE"}.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"24 File 1" Link "I-gad-24_File_1"} and @{"24 File 2" Link "I-gad-24_File_2"} gadgets can now be left blank to
               use the @{"File One" Link "I-gad-File_One"} and @{"File Two" Link "I-gad-File_Two"} names.

             @{b}*@{ub} MakeInfo 1.55 used. This doc now has more formatting.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"Progress" Link "Req-Progress"} requester now shows a list view of messages.

        @{b}*@{ub} Bug Fixes

             @{b}*@{ub} Image remapping should be more correct.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"Edit/Mode" Link "CI-men-E-EMode"} sub-menu has a capital @{b}E@{ub}.

             @{b}*@{ub} Should no longer leave the Screen with the incorrect
               @{"palette" Link "P-CHANGEPALETTE"} when @{b}TSMorph@{ub} is quit.

             @{b}*@{ub} Fixed a nasty memory corruption bug with @{"DX" Link "P-DX"} and @{"DY" Link "P-DY"}.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"Control Window gadgets" Link "Con-gad"} now look more correct on screens
               with more than 4 colours.

             @{b}*@{ub} Fixed a bug where @{"parameters" Link "Par-TSMorph"} were automatically reset
               when opening a project.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"Open Points..." Link "CI-men-P-Open"} no longer resets Morph parameters.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"Load Settings..." Link "men-S-LoadS"} now works.

             @{b}*@{ub} @{"DEPTH" Link "P-DEPTH"} parameter can now be greater than the number of
               points without memory corruption.

             @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}TSMorph@{ub} window is correctly disabled when saving
               after @{"Unsaved Project" Link "Req-Unsaved"} requester is displayed.

             @{b}*@{ub} Uses less memory for @{"Zoom" Link "P-ZOOM"} raster.

             @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}TSMorph@{ub} opens @{b}amigaguide@{ub} window on screen specified
               by @{"PUBSCREEN" Link "P-PUBSCREEN"}.

             @{b}*@{ub} String requesters will now accept empty strings.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 2.0a

        @{b}*@{ub} Minor update to the @{"File Format" Link "File_Format"} description. (Includes Anim
          Morphs and Warps).

        @{b}*@{ub}     @{b}ENV/TSMorph/def_points@{ub} now has Stack set to 8192.
          (Prevents crashes when using @{b}opal.library@{ub}).

        @{b}*@{ub} @{"Render Public Screen" Link "P-PUBSCREENR"} menu item is disabled if
          @{b}reqtools.library@{ub} is not available. (Previously crashed if
          selected).

        @{b}*@{ub} Only relevant @{"OPENMODE" Link "P-OPENMODE"} is ALWAYS if @{b}opal.library@{ub} is not
          available (Thanks to spark@cix).

        @{b}*@{ub} Screen is automatically brought to the front when the first
          window opens.


@EndNode

@Node "Hints" "TSMorph.guide/Hints"
@Next "Distribution"
@Prev "History"
@Toc "Main"

Hints & Tips
************

This section supplies some hopefully useful information which may not
be immediately apparent elsewhere.

@{b}Speed?@{ub}

If you do not have an FPU then set the INTEGER parameter to YES.  Even
if you do have an FPU this may still make things run faster.

If it still slow then try changing DX and DY to 1 (or more).

If you have lots of memory then setting the precalculate part of MODE
(16) should help.

@{b}What MODE?@{ub}

This depends on the type of Morph.

If you are, say, rotating some text on a background, then it is
probably best to set the stationary part (1). You would NOT want to set
the precalculate once part (16).

If you are morphing, say, two faces where the points do not move much
between the first and last image then it may be best to set the
precalculate part (16) (provided you have enough free memory). Setting
the Delaunay part (8) may also be a good idea.

Setting search (2) is probably not a good idea.

@{b}Not enough memory for TSMorph@{ub}

If you run out of Chip memory when trying to load large images then try
setting ZOOM to OFF.

@{b}HAM output has fringing@{ub}

A very simple algorithm is used for generating HAM output. If the
output is not acceptable then the best idea is to output some other
format (ILBM24 or PPM) and then run a proper image conversion program
on the output (possibly as part of the Postscript script).


@EndNode

