@Node "TSMorph-prefs" "TSMorph.guide/TSMorph-prefs"
@Toc "Par"

Preferences editor
******************

@{b}TSMorph-prefs@{ub} is a standard preferences editor.

When loaded it loads the current @{"settings" Link "Par"} from
@{b}ENV:TSMorph/TSMorph.prefs@{ub}.  It then displays a window showing all
the preferences.

@{b}Help@{ub} displays context sensitive help using @{b}amigaguide@{ub} if available.


 @{" Gadgets " Link "TSMP-gad"}         Gadgets displayed in the Preferences Window
 @{" Menus   " Link "TSMP-men"}         Menus available in the Preferences Window


@EndNode

@Node "TSMP-gad" "TSMorph.guide/TSMP-gad"
@Next "TSMP-men"
@Toc "TSMorph-prefs"

TSMorph-prefs Gadgets
=====================

@font topaz.font 8

     ----------------------------------------------------------
     |@{"." Link "TSMP-Close"}| TSMorph Preferences                             |@{" " Link "TSMP-Zoom"}|@{" " Link "TSMP-Depth"}|
