@EndNode

@Node "TSMP-Save" "TSMorph.guide/TSMP-Save"
@Next "TSMP-Use"
@Toc "TSMP-gad"

TSMorph-prefs Save gadget
-------------------------

This save the @{"settings" Link "Par"} in @{b}ENV:TSMorph/TSMorph.prefs@{ub} and
@{b}ENVARC:TSMorph/TSMorph.prefs@{ub}.

Any changes are not picked up until @{b}TSMorph@{ub} or @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub} is
reloaded.


@EndNode

@Node "TSMP-Use" "TSMorph.guide/TSMP-Use"
@Next "TSMP-Cancel"
@Prev "TSMP-Save"
@Toc "TSMP-gad"

TSMorph-prefs Use gadget
------------------------

This save the @{"settings" Link "Par"} in @{b}ENV:TSMorph/TSMorph.prefs@{ub}.

Any changes are not picked up until @{b}TSMorph@{ub} or @{b}TSMorph-render@{ub} is
reloaded.


@EndNode

