@Next "TSMP-men-P-Quit"
@Prev "TSMP-men-P-Open"
@Toc "TSMP-men-Project"

TSMorph-prefs Project/Save As... menu item
..........................................

This displays a file requester to save the @{"settings" Link "Par"}. The default name
is @{b}TSMorph.prefs@{ub} in the current directory.


@EndNode

